                     <interp inst="t18300114-173-person1192" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a pawnbroker. I have two pairs of shoes pawned on the 19th of December by Redman, and some on the 14th - I cannot be certain who brought those.</p>
