             on Redman - he said he did not know how it came in his pocket.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Major's Defence. I never pawned nor had a pair of shoes.</p>
               <p>Redman's Defence. I know nothing about them.</p>
               <p>
            
